8. Privacy Interpretation
Strong Privacy
ε < 1
High privacy protection with larger utility degradation.
Moderate Privacy
1 ≤ ε ≤ 5
Balanced privacy-utility trade-off.
Weak Privacy
ε > 10
Lower privacy protection with higher predictive utility.
